<br>
It is a safe spot, if I remember it right and understand Fey correctly, in the sense that it's out of aggro range of roamers and spawn points. <br>
<br>
However, if you pull a critter to that location and fight it there and if a roamer come close enough to be within aggro range, it will have no trouble coming up to you and beat your face in. :)<br>
<br>
So, it's not an exploit in any way shape or form. There are plenty of places in any dungeon in EQ where it's safe for you to sit down and med and/or pulling single to and fight without being attacked/ganged upon.<br>
<br>
Flamiously Yours,<br>
