<br>
1) When a mob is agro and has no ability to get to you however you can attack it (cast or whatever) and kill it<br>
<br>
2) when no wandering mobs or mobs around you &quot;see you&quot; therefore dont agro therefor its a safe spot. however when a mob is agro going to this spot does not stop the mob from following you and hitting you.<br>
<br>
1 = exploit <br>
2 = part of the game<br>
<br>
His post = 2<br>
<br>
Tils<br>
